      <title>泰国顶级廉价航空公司预计 2024 年核心利润将创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/top-thai-budget-carrier-expects-2024-core-profit-to-hit-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最大廉价航空公司的所有者亚洲航空预计，随着海外游客激增推动机票需求和票价上涨，今年核心业务盈利将创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/top-thai-budget-carrier-expects-2024-core-profit-to-hit-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
